name: Magician of Black Chaos Supreme
effect:
Must first be Fusion Summoned by banishing 1 "Magician of Black Chaos" from your field, and cannot be Fusion Summoned by other ways.
This card is always treated as "Magician of Black Chaos."
You can only Special Summon "Magician of Black Chaos Supreme" once per turn.
When your opponent activates a card or effect (Quick Effect): You can negate the activation, and if you do, banish that card. You can only activate this effect once per turn.
